---
title: Easy Double BBQ Chicken Burger & Onion Chutney with Creamy Slaw & Fries
description: Quick juicy chicken seasoned with a barbecue zap is a smokey dream come true for your taste buds. Place it between two buns, serve with classic fries and glaze the chicken with an onion chutney to elevate these burgers to the next level.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ab3e63ce6b1bd057254df8-f232e0e9.jpeg
